I recently went to the Champs-√âlys√©es with my daughter following an invitation, but I would like to express my deep disappointment with the reception we received. When checking our tickets, the person in charge made fun of our last name, which made us very uncomfortable. This behavior is unacceptable, especially since my daughter suffers from agoraphobia.
